Package triviaMaze.maze

Class LinkedRectangularMaze

java.lang.Object
triviaMaze.maze.LinkedRectangularMaze
All Implemented Interfaces:
IMaze
public class LinkedRectangularMaze
extends java.lang.Object
implements IMaze
An implementation of IMaze in which the maze is rectangular in structure, the start is in the top left, and the end is in the bottom right
Author:
Jacob Erdman
